			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				As a means to control mana usage, keep both Healing and Greater Healing memed for a while. Heal heals around 80 and Greater Heal around 300, so there's quite a gap in between. If you are healing, say 100, just use normal Healing. This is particularly important in a group where you'll be healing many members; don't just use Greater Healing on everyone everytime they need heal, you'll go oom in no time :) Later on though, Healing just becomes not good enough, and that's when you finally stop using normal Healing.
				</font>
			</td>

